songs.title: All In (Unreleased)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]
We address luggage
Was depressed, we protect black women
Keep ya breath, we don't project bullshit
Flee the nets, fear of exposure
Feed the guests, peel them fresh onions
Feet that kept runnin'
See the man tryna split my conscious
But we done handled some bigger monsters
Why need the hands? I'm eating regardless
I had a prayer up with different gods
I know the tapestry is enormous
Patchin' a straw in it
I know the path battle with darkness
I hold a match up and take it all in

[Hook]
Patchin' a straw in it
I know the path battle with darkness
I hold a match up and take it all in
I'm all in
Yeah, I'm all in
All in
All in
All in
Yeah, I'm all in
I hold a match up and take it all in
